country=E2=80=99s total territory.</p>
<p style=3D"line-height:24px;color:#2A3034;margin:1em 0">However, in recent=
 years, the Druze have rediscovered their Arab identity, and some are now s=
keptical of Israel=E2=80=99s intentions. Many see Israel=E2=80=99s recent a=
ctions in Syria as part of Netanyahu=E2=80=99s broader plan to transform th=
e Middle East. They don=E2=80=99t buy Israel=E2=80=99s attempt to present i=
tself as their protector; they believe its real goal is to establish an all=
iance of regional minorities dominated by Israel.</p>
<p style=3D"line-height:24px;color:#2A3034;margin:1em 0"><strong>Foundation=
